<div class="clause">
  <span class="num">32.</span> <span class="clause-title">TENANT ESTOPPEL CERTIFICATE:</span>
  Tenant shall execute and return a tenant estoppel certificate delivered to Tenant by Landlord or Landlord&rsquo;s
