  correct, and may be relied upon by a lender or purchaser.
</div>

<div class="clause">
  <span class="num">33.</span> <span class="clause-title">JOINT AND INDIVIDUAL OBLIGATIONS:</span>
  If there is more than one Tenant, each one shall be individually and completely responsible for the performance
  of all obligations of Tenant under this Agreement, jointly with every other Tenant, and individually, whether
  or not in possession.
</div>

